from_name.x: Cynthia Bradley
message.x:
Paid Research for People with Rheumatoid Arthritis (taking Enbrel, Humira, SmartJect, Remicade, or Orencia), Ankylosing Spondylitis, Psoriatic Arthritis, Ulcerative Colitis, their Caregivers, and Nurses in Rheumatology. 

Date: October 2014
Compensation: $150 Cash
Time commitment: (1) 30-minute session
Location: San Jose, CA, Saratoga, CA, or San Francisco, CA

Interface Analysis Associates (IAA) is a Bay Area health care consumer research firm that conducts usability studies for medical devices and drug delivery systems. Our research helps to create patient-centered products that are safer, easier to learn, and more enjoyable to use. In our studies, we let you simulate use of a new device, procedure, or set of instructions and ask for your feedback and preferences. Everything is simulated in our studies- you are never asked to take any drug, injection, etc.

If you are interested in contributing to the design of future medication delivery devices and want to get paid for your input, please contact us today at (408) 907-6866 or email us at: iaa_research@yahoo.com. Please include your name, telephone number, and refer to the "RA Study."

Thank you.
